config CDR
	bool "CDR (Common Data Representation) serialization library"
	help
	  Little-endian CDR codec for encoding and decoding DDS/ROS 2 rmw
	  payloads, as used by zenoh-pico ROS bridges. Provides the primitive
	  layer (scalars, strings, encapsulation header); message layouts are
	  assembled by the application on top.
